Juſtice, if this be blaſphemy: If to perſtringe and ſharply rebuke with all Miniſterial authority (yet humble and diſcreetly) the baſe Policies, and injurious practiſes of an Adulterous generation, of a ſacrilegious crue▪ and God-robbing faction; who make w • y for the intereſts of their factions, and for their private honors or eſtates; by threatning, impriſoning, and at laſt murthering their King;
